    <body>&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Welcome to the Honeywell
Aerospace IDEA Exchange.&amp;nbsp; The IDEA Exchange provides a forum to allow ALL
Aerospace employees to get involved and participate in the success of the
business.&amp;nbsp; You can provide suggestions for improvements to products,
services or processes that would help drive revenue growth, increase
productivity or improve the customer experience.&amp;nbsp; In addition submitting
ideas, you can vote and comment on your favorite ideas to ensure they rise to
the top.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Here are some basic
guidelines for submitting ideas to the IDEA Exchange&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:
Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;Make sure your idea is reasonable and necessary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt; – if you are not sure or cannot articulate the value the
improvement would drive do not submit at this time; you can always come back at
a later time.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:
Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;Search for your IDEA before you submit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt; – keep your community clean and productivity by
searching before you post.&amp;nbsp; Make a concerted effort to locate similar
ideas and, if they are located, comment on them or suggests merges.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:
Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;Make Title meaningful &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;-
Titles like &quot;product improvement&quot; offer other members little idea of
what your Idea is about. Include product name, specific functions/business
processes as well as a brief notion of the issue/limitation&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:
Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;Be clear and concise&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;
- When posting and idea, put other members in the best position to judge and respond
to them.&amp;nbsp; Clearly state the specific issue your idea recommends
addressing/enhancing. At the same time, make your post reader-friendly by
keeping your idea to a few clear sentences.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:
Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;5.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;If possible, picture it&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:
#1F497D&quot;&gt; - Everybody loves colors! Make pretty pictures if you have the time.
Conveying your idea visually allows community members to better envision your
proposal and will lead to more promotions&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;
mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:
Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;6.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;Be respectful&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt; - A
successful community is built upon an open flow of dialogue. It is just as
important to critique suggestions as it is to promote them. However, remember
that we all seek a stronger more robust Aerospace environment and demeaning,
insulting activity only serves to impede that effort. Always keep in mind, it&apos;s
about Honeywell, not about yourself.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F497D&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Ready to submit an IDEA?&amp;nbsp;
Click &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/ideas/editIdea.apexp?c=09a3000000052pq&amp;amp;retURL=%2Fideas%2FideaList.apexp&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;HERE&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;to get started…&lt;/font&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</body>
